author: @danieletaddei3577
text: I want to congratulate Tzuyu again for her solo debut (amazing album) and for having worked really hard for her debut. These specials make us understand once again how much hard work there is behind a song, a video clip, a choreography. I really appreciated that Tzuyu was distracted with hiking (a fantastic place outside of Seoul . And thank you for introducing me to it and I hope I can go and visit it), the trip to the sea, the lunch with her mother and friends (memorable moment), And then I loved the support of all the members of the band. I think this gave her more confidence. And also the fact that she was surrounded by people ready to help her and support her is a wonderful thing. I think her solo debut made her even more confident, helped her overcome her shyness a bit (but let's be honest, we also love her shy and reserved side that she sometimes has). I'm really happy for her and her debut went very well (but I never had any doubts about it). Thanks Tzuyu for your incredible work and thanks precious diamond for always shining so bright. Fighting💖
